=======
Changes
=======

* 0.64:   huTools.structured.dict2xml now supports flat lists and unordered content
* 0.63:   huTools.cache added
* 0.62:   huTools.structured.Struct has a __nonzero__ method
* 0.61:   huTools.structured.Struct and make_struct handle lists and get an items() method
* 0.61:   huTools.structured.Struct and make_struct handle lists and get an items() method
* 0.60p1: huTools.http implements authentication
* 0.60:   huTools.http API and function-based pyJasper Interface. Dependencie Reduction

          This version introduces a HTTP-API menat to allow easy use on pure Python and AppEngine plattforms.
          All other huTools modules should reley on them instead of httplib2 and others.

          pyjasper now comes with an non Object Oriented interface and also strips timestamps from generated
          PDFs to ensure the same input generates EXACTLY the same output.

          use hujson instead of simplejson, alsp big cleanup, github-tools/paver for documentation, better
          documentation at http://hudora.github.com/huTools/ , hujson, rework of the structured module, Python
          2.5, Google AppEngine compabitility (also in hujson), reduced dependencies, http - a simple http
          client, unified credential configuration for postmark and jasper, support for signing in pyJasper,
* 0.53p2: calendar.formats.convert_to_datetime() added convert_to_date() is more robust now
* 0.53p1: Bugfix for _convert_dict_to_xml_recurse: Do not translate None to 'None'
* 0.53:   poster_encode contains Chris AtLee's code for form upload
* 0.52p1  Ported JasperGenerator.get_report from pyJasper
* 0.52:   postmark API client - see http://postmarkapp.com/
* 0.51    pyjasper - Client for the pyJasper toolkit
* 0.50:   monetary - easy but often used monetary functions
* 0.49:   depreciated huTools.protocols, removed huTools.struct
* 0.48:   renamed struct to structured, luids.guid128() now uses uuid1
* 0.47p1: struct now can handle copy.copy()
* 0.47:   huTools.rest.Client - a basic REST client
* 0.46:   Function for retrieving the index of the week for a date
* 0.45:   Function for rounding / truncating date(time) objects
* 0.44:   Code Quality checks: reindent.py & pep8.py
* 0.43p1: xmltools.encode_text unterstuetzt jetzt callables
* 0.43:   Code zur Berechnung und Validierung von IBAN
* 0.40:   added NetStringIO
* 0.39p3: Version Number bumped for fix in [6688] (RO)
* 0.39p2: added obfuscation.RC4
* 0.39p1: added daemon.daemonize
* 0.39:   added humessaging, uniciode.deUmlaut, cleanup
* 0.38p4: luids.guid128() for generating a 26 character GUIDs
* 0.38p3: calendar.formats functions now default to the current time 
* 0.38p1: fixed caching, removed mobotix.py
* 0.38:   add mobotix.py (jdiemer)
* 0.37p1: added Israel
* 0.37:   Added async.Future and decorators.cache_function
* 0.36:   renamed io0 to int_or_0 and added io0 as a wrapper with a deprecation warning
* 0.35:   robusttypecasts module added
* 0.34:   checksumming.verify_ean() calendar.add_workdays_german(), decorators.memoize,  decorators.method_once() and decorators.func_once() added,
